11189896967,"Apr 15, 2024, 2:04:03 PM",2024 Boston Marathon,Run,"This was a lifetime goal to run this race. Sometimes to Win is to get to the starting line and finish.  Today was one of those days. No it did not go to plan- but I’m still so proud of this run. My gratitude is to the Somerville Road Runners and everyone who came out to help cheer me on. I can confidently say this was the hardest day for sport in my life but also one of the most rewarding.  I’ll be back!

