12647982990,"Oct 13, 2024, 12:39:42 PM",Chicago Marathon 2024,Run,"Awesome experience racing my 2nd world major and first time at Chicago. Had a great opening half in 1:26, but made the tough on-course decision to dial things down a little after mile 16 as I wanted to keep a controlled effort and I could feel trouble on the horizon. While it wasn’t quite the big “breakthrough” race I was hoping for, but still proud with this 3:03 finish and managed to not stop or walk when things got tough! 

